This directory contains version 3.1 of SB-Prolog.  It has
essentially the functionality of version 2.5, but has been
rewritten so that it runs on alignment-restricted processors
like Sun-4, Pyramid-98x, and SGI Iris.  

User manual: a Latex version is available in latex_doc.tar.Z,
a troff version (with -me macros) in sbprolog_doc.me.

